# Demo of the ShotDs Smart Cell

```elixir
Mix.install([
  {:kino_shot_ds, "~> 0.1"}
])
```

## TPTP Parser

<!-- livebook:{"attrs":"eyJjb250ZXh0X3N0ciI6IiIsImZvcm11bGFfc3RyIjoiIVtYIDogJG9dOiBYID0+IFgiLCJtb2RlIjoiZm9ybXVsYSIsInByb2JsZW1fc3RyIjoidGhmKHRlc3QsIGNvbmplY3R1cmUsICR0cnVlID0+ICR0cnVlKS4iLCJ0aGVtZSI6IkRyYWN1bGEiLCJ2YXJfbmFtZSI6InBhcnNlZF9mb3JtdWxhX29yX3Byb2JsZW0ifQ","chunks":null,"kind":"Elixir.KinoShotDs.TptpParser","livebook_object":"smart_cell"} -->

```elixir
problem = "thf(test, conjecture, $true => $true)."

parsed_formula_or_problem =
  case ShotDs.Tptp.parse_tptp_string(problem) do
    {:ok, parsed} -> parsed
    {:error, reason} -> raise "Error: #{inspect(reason)}"
  end

:ok
```

```elixir
parsed_formula_or_problem |> ShotDs.Util.Formatter.format!(false) |> IO.puts
```
